{"tid":2303234,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"平心而論 Spider-Man 3算唔算係近廿年最好睇嘅英雄片？","createTime":"2020-11-27T18:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T01:46:42.000Z","uid":5190,"like":38,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7229a9bc072f4ea120b3b4033e15bf1ff0700276","tid":2303234,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:17:13.000Z","msg":"首先 我知一定有人話avengers一定係最好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但淨係計劇情鋪排 tobey 版淨係用三集就可以將三位主角繪畫得出神入化 深入觀眾心 而avengers 前前後後加埋唔同英雄嘅片都起碼超過十集 已經唔可以相提並論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以 淨係單一咁講一個英雄先<br />\n<br />\nSpider man 3用短短兩粒鐘就完美帶出主題「Revenge and forgiveness 」由一切安穩到遇到種種問題而墜入黑暗 到最後放手去願諒他人 簡直係無與倫比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n短短一個畫面就帶出莫大嘅道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俗語有話 要贏人先要贏自己 但套電影就教我地 要願諒別人 先要願諒自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JV_Kov0E8j8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJV_Kov0E8j8&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Ci%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=280f53ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JV_Kov0E8j8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感情線方面 MJ 同Peter兩方都完美表達出作為英雄同平凡人嘅代溝 學aunt May 所講 兩個人嘅感情唔係只建立於單純嘅愛情 當中包括接納對方嘅缺點同包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙人線方面 可以睇出並唔係每個壞人都百分之百壞 而係世間上有種種原因驅使到一個人走向絕路 作為超級英雄嘅你 會選擇報復 定係原諒？有啲時候 我地有血有肉嘅人 的確會俾憤怒蒙蔽雙眼 而聆聽 係一個最適合嘅選擇 forgive yourself <br />\n<br />\n友情線方面 一路以嚟Harry同Peter都係好朋友 到第二集揭穿咗原來最好嘅朋友係殺父仇人 被憤怒蒙蔽雙眼嘅Harry 即使好友有求於佢都莫視 睇到最後Harry死個幕真係有少少感動到喊出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「none of that matter Peter,you are my friend!」<br />\n「best friend!」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gER_Oisdv7Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgER_Oisdv7Y&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Ci%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=201dec55\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gER_Oisdv7Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明白 演員都係一套電影成與敗嘅關鍵 但你唔可以講佢做依個角色做得唔好 又唔可以話做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撇除選角嘅因素同當時嘅cgi spider man 3的確係一套近廿年嚟最好嘅英雄片 淨係問邊個係你心目中嘅spider man 我諗好多人都會答 Tobey Maguire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622b4615742aa3d03a6b7b189448fc8fc1e9bf3e","tid":2303234,"uid":224351,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"Spiderman 2,3 (初代) &gt; Batman 2 (初代) &gt; Ironman 1"},{"pid":"dcc88aaffae290ea3aea9480bf6d56b6264ad3e8","tid":2303234,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622b4615742aa3d03a6b7b189448fc8fc1e9bf3e","tid":2303234,"uid":224351,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"Spiderman 2,3 (初代) &gt; Batman 2 (初代) &gt; Ironman 1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b848a7b744f948452f708e1a094bb66ae66380e","tid":2303234,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622b4615742aa3d03a6b7b189448fc8fc1e9bf3e","tid":2303234,"uid":224351,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"Spiderman 2,3 (初代) &gt; Batman 2 (初代) &gt; Ironman 1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:24:04.000Z","msg":"你個Batman 2 (初代) 係咪初到入40年前果堆？"},{"pid":"a65a65df1c91deb4c207fb966f380b7bd0d5ab1c","tid":2303234,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"5b848a7b744f948452f708e1a094bb66ae66380e","tid":2303234,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"622b4615742aa3d03a6b7b189448fc8fc1e9bf3e","tid":2303234,"uid":224351,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:21:10.000Z","msg":"Spiderman 2,3 (初代) &gt;